    ns1:otherInformation """In this course, and in case of any eventuality, although it will be a small group of students, every session could be moved to online teaching through Teams or Collaborate via Moodle. Uncertainty is rather high at the moment this guide is being validated, but everything has been defined to switch from unperson teaching to online sessions automatically.
The subject is related to SDGs 1, 4, 8, 9, 10 and 12."""@es ;
